{
  "stem": "26731.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You see more or less, what happened at that time, Jews from the East, Shanghai, stayed in the Western part of the United States.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the people coming in from the East, the eastern part, and what happened in the various cities, each family service took so-and-so many refugees.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I came, come the day of interview.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well he talked to me, well, where would you like to go, to Detroit or Saint Paul?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, I knew enough about the United States, that I'll go to Saint Paul.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Lo and behold, they put me on-- it was most interesting in New York for the first time going around.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was so grateful to my English teachers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At least I could make myself understood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some people arrived that actually didn't know any English.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think, well, waiting there in Bremen, waiting for the boat to come, they had courses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some people, ah, we don't bother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We learn in the country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wonder how they managed coming over here and didn't know one word of English.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But probably you always find someone who speak Germany and Yiddish, probably they get along, too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But in New York, it was quite interesting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the middle of the night, the stores were open.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And actually I enjoyed the short stay in New York.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They put me on the Trail Blazer on the trip to Saint Paul.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I missed the connective train in Saint Paul.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The tourists, they said, look.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the afternoon Train 2 takes a number of hours.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why don't you go downtown?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You take a bus downtown.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Do not run around the neighborhood if you have a nice coat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's not a very good neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Go to the bus stop.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Take a bus.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Go downtown.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Come back [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
